items.name: case circularSmall
items.desc: A small circular area that ClockKit displays on the Color watch face.

items.name: case extraLarge
items.desc: A large square area that ClockKit displays on the X-Large watch face.

items.name: case modularSmall
items.desc: A small square area that ClockKit displays on the Modular watch face.

items.name: case modularLarge
items.desc: A large rectangular area that ClockKit displays on the Modular watch face.

items.name: case utilitarianSmall
items.desc: A small square or rectangular area that ClockKit Displays on the Utility, Mickey, Chronograph, and Simple watch faces.

items.name: case utilitarianSmallFlat
items.desc: A small rectangular area that ClockKit Displays on the Photos, Motion, and Timelapse watch faces.

items.name: case utilitarianLarge
items.desc: A large rectangular area that spans the width of the screen in the Utility and Mickey watch faces.

items.name: case graphicCorner
items.desc: A curved area that fills the corners in the Infograph watch face.

items.name: case graphicCircular
items.desc: A circular area that ClockKit displays on the Infograph and Infograph Modular watch faces.

items.name: case graphicBezel
items.desc: A circular area with optional curved text that ClockKit displays along the bezel of the Infograph watch face.

items.name: case graphicRectangular
items.desc: A large rectangular area that ClockKit displays in the center of the Infograph Modular watch face.

items.name: case graphicExtraLarge
items.desc: A large square area that ClockKit displays on the X-Large watch face.

items.name: typealias CLKComplicationFamily.AllCases
items.desc: Returns an array that contains all the complication families.

items.name: static var allCases: [CLKComplicationFamily]
items.desc: An array that contains all the complication families.
